kremotecontrol: kremotecontrol (KDE frontend for your remote controls)
kremotecontrol:
kremotecontrol: KRemoteControl (formerly known as KDELirc) is a KDE frontend for your
kremotecontrol: remote controls. It allows to configure actions for button presses on
kremotecontrol: remotes. All types of remotes supported by the Solid module in the KDE
kremotecontrol: platform are also supported by KRemoteControl (e.g. with the Linux
kremotecontrol: Infrared Remote Control system (LIRC) as backend).
kremotecontrol:
kremotecontrol: http://www.kde.org
